{"tid":895183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本社畜太慘！火車站內設「迷你辦公室」，上司急call也能秒上工  原文網址: 日本社畜太慘！火車站內設「迷你辦公室」","createTime":"2018-11-09T03:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T04:43:09.000Z","uid":1121,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed30eedaa83a9e0e564ac89295facc800c7d89e5","tid":895183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"雖然台灣的薪資水準與工時已經讓人覺得夠悲慘，但想必大家也同意，如果問全世界已開發國家中，勞工過得最慘的國家是哪個......你也會毫不猶豫地回答日本。<br />\n<br />\n在部分歐洲國家已經頒布「下班後不准LINE員工」、「下班時間不准寄公務信」等等禁令的同時，這下可好，日本人選擇的則是「讓員工可以在火車站裡工作」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3676/3676706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3676%2F3676706.jpg&h=d4185c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／JR東日本的實行規劃示意圖） <br />\n<br />\nJR東日本鐵路公司日前宣布，將會推出命名為「STATION WORK」的共享空間辦公室業務，從11月28日開始試行，主要先以「個人間」的形式推廣，日後也會推出空間較大、可讓數人一同討論事情的小會議室。<br />\n<br />\n到時候人們可以透過掃描QRcode來進出房間、計費也是用多少收多少的計時制，而室內設施五臟俱全，包含桌椅、照明、插座、免費Wi-Fi、USB插孔、冷暖氣與空調等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3676/3676705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3676%2F3676705.jpg&h=5a975bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然對於創業者來說，車站內有這樣的空間或許真的很方便（例如夥伴一同約在車站、直接就能開工等等），但考慮到日本的工作環境與社會風氣，再加上JR主推的是個人間，其實也不難想像，這種服務其實是因應「日本勞工常常被臨時急call、需要地方工作」而誕生的。<br />\n<br />\n這個「STATION WORK」會先在東京、品川、新宿這三個大站試行，即使方便歸方便，花枝還是想說......日本人真的好慘啊嗚嗚。"},{"pid":"c91c30159d2581e8545f9c4919876dd6ad285a8d","tid":895183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925221ba15793ef2205e1f90080707d220c24033","tid":895183,"uid":4693,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"AV 個D 扑野網吧姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bef18afe8845fa8577f513bd5a566a8b571c9bf","tid":895183,"uid":59972,"like":23,"dislike":7,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">計費也是用多少收多少</span>的計時制，而室內設施五臟俱全，包含桌椅、照明、插座、<span style=\"color: red;\">免費Wi-Fi</span>、USB插孔、冷暖氣與空調等等<br />\n<br />\n比咗錢仲算唔算免費"},{"pid":"0c3010acd9b3b362662e3121dd1c25e23d977a69","tid":895183,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"可以隨時入去出火喎，正呀話"},{"pid":"dfa759137483eb256f62f1c6c554bec3877dd413","tid":895183,"uid":103207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"925221ba15793ef2205e1f90080707d220c24033","tid":895183,"uid":4693,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"AV 個D 扑野網吧姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"條仔係出面,女朋友係入面俾人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f93b7d3306b333f4070b0da9908c900557a50a7","tid":895183,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"就算無「迷你辦公室」, <br />\n都要用手提電腦 / 電話覆公司EMAIL啦"},{"pid":"1958671254b5fd9f7bdea21f778a30199d8d2c05","tid":895183,"uid":194415,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://store.happytifyold.com/uploads/2017-11-20/B01ED0D5ABE2.Jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.happytifyold.com%2Fuploads%2F2017-11-20%2FB01ED0D5ABE2.Jpeg&h=59275b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmatch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6889d6cd124cd3a90cb7df5c1423adf5149a3f4d","tid":895183,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:07:37.000Z","msg":"唔去m記?"},{"pid":"db8c0346e52fea435dd78be22e4d1bc81d4a2184","tid":895183,"uid":79563,"like":15,"